{"tid":17640,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"■■ PSV機主討論區無人開!■■===============(1)","createTime":"2016-12-02T02:05:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T17:15:22.000Z","uid":48620,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5af838955f6b444846101d3f14ae069ef9b02473","tid":17640,"uid":48620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T02:05:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">◆最新情報</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Q4DMzXa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQ4DMzXa.jpg&h=f4f96305&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS PLUS知識 <br />\n<a href=\"http://bbs.a9vg.com/thread-2319874-1-1.html \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbbs.a9vg.com%2Fthread-2319874-1-1.html%20&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=f57be163\" target=\"_blank\">http://bbs.a9vg.com/thread-2319874-1-1.html </a><br />\n<br />\n最新中文化遊戲 <br />\n<a href=\"http://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60547&amp;snA=22758&amp;tnum=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D60547%26snA%3D22758%26tnum%3D1&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=143434f0\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60547&amp;snA=22758&amp;tnum=1</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/EmA0knd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FEmA0knd.png&h=08d7d0fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6fa3abac62b53e490b2af5aafa9fc5d3b52a1a6e","tid":17640,"uid":48620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T02:06:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">Q&amp;A </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins>買機有咩留意? </ins><br />\n檢查下所有掣，analog用唔用到 <br />\n個mon有冇好多死點有冇邊d位感應唔到（藍店冇記錯要五點先肯換） <br />\n另外檢查下配件齊唔齊 <br />\n<a href=\"http://asia.playstation.com/hk/cht/psv/hardware#bundle\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fasia.playstation.com%2Fhk%2Fcht%2Fpsv%2Fhardware%23bundle&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=6129342c\" target=\"_blank\">http://asia.playstation.com/hk/cht/psv/hardware#bundle</a> <br />\n試game就試內置既welcome park，應該用齊哂psv既功能 <br />\n機套、保謢貼、保謢殼就自行選擇 <br />\n<br />\n<ins>水貨定行貨，邊度出機好? </ins><br />\n水貨比行貨平但冇保養 <br />\n行貨就買機時有一年保養 <br />\n水貨由於冇保養建議去返比較出名既game鋪買 <br />\n行貨就建議去platinum shop(藍店)買 <br />\n<a href=\"http://asia.playstation.com/hk/cht/support/wheretoshop\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fasia.playstation.com%2Fhk%2Fcht%2Fsupport%2Fwheretoshop&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=5d396297\" target=\"_blank\">http://asia.playstation.com/hk/cht/support/wheretoshop</a> <br />\n會多90日保養 <br />\n主動check機基本上邊間都一樣 <br />\n<br />\n<ins>1000定2000機好? </ins><br />\n1000機較平、mon色較靚等 <br />\n2000機較薄、較輕、轉左usb接口位、內置1GB位、續航力較大、mon冇烙印等 <br />\n詳細比較請自己google，有大量文章/比較圖參考 <br />\n另外要留意sony有咩出機優惠 <br />\n<br />\n<ins>記憶卡買幾大好，8/16/32/64GB? </ins><br />\n依家一隻$3xx~$4xx既game大約係2至2.5GB <br />\n$1xx左右既下載game大約500MB至1GB <br />\n按自己需要選擇返 <br />\n假如你係ps plus會員經驗之談就最少16GB <br />\n<br />\n<ins>game應該買日版定行版好? </ins><br />\npsv冇用過鎖區所以唔需要擔心部機玩唔到日版/行版 <br />\n所以買咩版主要睇你用咩psn <br />\n因為依家既game普遍都連code送各類野 <br />\n日版code就要用日psn先用到 <br />\n行版就港psn先用到 <br />\n如果你係冇開過任何psn就睇下面條問題 <br />\n<br />\n<ins>psn開日本定香港區好? </ins><br />\n如果你主要玩中文或者熱門game就開香港psn <br />\n相反你玩開日文、較冷門或者想多d下載game選擇就開日本psn <br />\n日本psn只受JCB信用卡 <br />\n如果隻game冇online pass你用咩區既psn都會玩到online對戰 <br />\n假如有online pass就請買返自己psn對應既game版本"},{"pid":"c98a6809bea946471488ac29c1500ea44cb90e45","tid":17640,"uid":38113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T02:13:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ff976471551a3d64acbc1759aee8701bdb955b","tid":17640,"uid":48620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T02:23:25.000Z","msg":"近期必玩推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"