2F2016%2F12%2Fps-plus-2016%25e5%25b9%25b412%25e6%259c%2588%25e5%2585%258d%25e8%25b2%25bb%25e9%2581%258a%25e6%2588%25b2%2F&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=d151c380\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.asia.playstation.com/hk-cht/6839/2016/12/ps-plus-2016%e5%b9%b412%e6%9c%88%e5%85%8d%e8%b2%bb%e9%81%8a%e6%88%b2/</a>"},{"pid":"1f1753a3e3d82aac9bbffed26a499b625a2513c9","tid":17640,"uid":39457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T10:12:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>多數用黎remote ps4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n得720p 無咩快感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我想出部黎咁用 用玩每月免費遊戲會否不智</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得買部二手嘅都OK嘅,依家二手先喺700-800左右,玩完又可以放翻出去<br />\n<br />\n我本身買部二手PSV就喺打算拎嚟玩plus啲game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見佢之前又送討鬼同無雙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無雙到依家都仲未打爆,自己又買咗太鼓嚟玩"},{"pid":"9f0fd54feb57e2b00a59fb16dcd40464a3a2913b","tid":17640,"uid":31239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T16:19:39.000Z","msg":"岩岩入手咗部psv<br />\n想玩返基連之野望v<br />\n可以點down?"},{"pid":"ff0781c5cd5fb275ab576603ac49bf8b8a45b29f","tid":17640,"uid":61241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T16:25:18.000Z","msg":"其實12月出左新色<br />\nSONY官網都唔寫<br />\n香港部門係咪放棄PSV<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a02df91be3a17305039a64ac03fd81bfd6f6a84","tid":17640,"uid":31239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T16:36:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩入手咗部psv<br />\n想玩返基連之野望v<br />\n可以點down?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dVL8G64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https:/