"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T08:55:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>新人啱啱買咗部2000 想問下轉帳嘅問題<br />\n(1)如果想轉帳嘅話就要預備兩張記憶卡?<br />\n我依家果張係港帳,想轉日帳係咪要將港帳張卡抽出黎之後將部機恢復預設<br />\n重新開機再將新卡插入去就可以用到日帳?<br />\n(2) 以後想轉帳係咪都要重複(1)嘅步驟?<br />\n(3) 港帳/日帳down咗嘅DLC會唔會恢復預設之後就冇哂? 定已經save哂落張港帳/日帳卡度?<br />\n希望有巴打可以解答我嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感激不盡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1. 要兩張卡， format 機後插卡登入<br />\n2. 係， 唔想成日format 就買兩部機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 唔會無就算唔少心del 左可dl 返，有插卡就會係save落張卡但係好似有極少量既game save 會save 落 game card度<br />\n<br />\n利申 : 兩部psv<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/a7d53e8n\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fa7d53e8n&h=a82b0daf&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該哂巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76f35d369184987ebcaeca0e7d66b223abf1c988","tid":17640,"uid":2502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:49:21.000Z","msg":"誠收一部psv2000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n約700-800蚊左右<br />\n如有意麻煩留言再議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6626c7c9efc73df1dba92b987b733ab5bc588c","tid":17640,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T21:47:20.000Z","msg":"討論"},{"pid":"05ad4a8a6424239be85c5e36c3dbe5f2898517f5","tid":17640,"uid":23700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T17:02:39.000Z","msg":"呢一刻PSV買新定二手好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n已經有一部PSV 1006 3G<br />\n<br />\n想買多一部2000機加 L2R2制 用日服專玩remote play FF14 同PSO2<br />\n<img src=\"http://s.pacn.ws/640/q6/remote-play-assist-attachment-for-playstation-vita-slim-471075.1.jpg?o6a6zz\" data-thumbnail-